name: Sculpt plate "Still Life with Basic Geometric Shapes" by Koloto
description: The work is dedicated to the artists who have not achieved what they want, and there are a lot of them and to whom I style myself. The plate presents the main still life from which many begin their creative path in drawing. I start but do not finish it for various reasons. Shedding a lot of blood sweat and wasting your precious time wasting your life. Often left with nothing and only after their departure are recognized.
